


convstr(1)                     Scilab Function                     convstr(1)






NAME
  convstr - case conversion

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [y]=convstr(str-matrix, ["flag"])

PARAMETERS

  str-matrix, y
            : matrices of strings

  "flag"    : string ("u" for upper or "l" for lower (default value))

DESCRIPTION
  converts the matrix of strings str-matrix into lower case (for "l" ;default
  value) or upper case (for "u").








































